 * | @ref simulators | Simulator interfaces and all backend implementations |
 * | @ref network | Distributed quantum computing — hosts, controllers, topology |
 * | @ref tensor_networks | Tensor network simulation and contraction strategies |
 * | @ref schedulers | Job scheduling and parallel execution |
